wiki.content: “LUNCH” by Billie Eilish is the lead single from her third studio album HIT ME HARD AND SOFT. The lyrics explore sexual themes, including expressions of sexual desire for another woman. This track emphasize physical attraction and lust, using food as a metaphor for consumption in a sexual context. Musically, the song follows a minimalist production, with Billie’s signature whispery, seductive vocal style, which adds to the sensual tone. The sexual nature of the lyrics paired with the sultry beats creates an atmosphere that is both daring and intimate, showcasing a more explicit side of Billie Eilish’s artistry. The song pushes boundaries both lyrically and emotionally, using suggestive language and metaphors to convey desire in a raw, unapologetic way. Read more on Last.fm.
